      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert a Ruby on Rails Web App to Mobile Apps</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Mobiloud can convert your Rails app into iOS and Android apps in just two weeks. Keep all your site functionality, build a better mobile UX!</p>
    </div>
